commit.message: Upd8 SMS.py with better message and error handling

Add question()s and reprompt()s when not enough info

One of requirements for certification is that the app leaves the session open
when asking for more information.
Prevent user from completing reminders not due yet (fixes #26)
Implement more of recurring reminder completions (fixes #24)
Return error message on unknown day_intervals
Make Alexa properly say phone number
Remove ability to set dates in the past (fixes #20)
Make more things work on Lambda
Make completion reminders sendable from all user_ids
Update divergence meter calculation to only use user tasks
Make it care about user_id and filter and such
Added SMS Completion Texts with DynamoDB
